<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta
      name="keywords"
      content="Mp3, songs, music, download, song downloader"
    />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Details about this web app, stacked used and download counter"
    />
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/about_project.css" />
    <title>About Project</title>
    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      html {
        height: 100%;
        width: 100%;
        font-size: 16px;
        background-color: #4a55a2;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .main {
        width: 90%;
        height: 100%;
        background-color: #7895cb;
        margin: auto;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 2px 0;
      }

      .main h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-family: "Trebuchet MS", "Lucida Sans Unicode", "Lucida Grande",
          "Lucida Sans", Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 3rem;
        color: #c5dff8;
      }

      .main p {
        margin: 3rem;
        font-family: "Lucida Sans", "Lucida Sans Regular", "Lucida Grande",
          "Lucida Sans Unicode", Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #c5dff8;
      }

      .main ul {
        margin: 3rem;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-family: "Gill Sans", "Gill Sans MT", Calibri, "Trebuchet MS",
          sans-serif;
        color: #c5dff8;
      }

      .main li {
        margin: 0 2rem;
      }

      .main ol {
        margin: 1rem 3rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
        color: #a0bfe0;
      }

      .headings {
        color: #4a55a2;
      }

      ol li {
        color: #c5dff8;
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 990px) {
        html {
          font-size: 12px;
        }
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 826px) {
        html {
          font-size: 10px;
        }
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 670px) {
        html {
          font-size: 10px;
        }
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 565px) {
        html {
          font-size: 10px;
        }
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 537px) {
        html {
          font-size: 10px;
        }
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 310px) {
        html {
          font-size: 10px;
        }
      }

      .download_container {
        background-color: rgba(255, 123, 0, 0.894);
        border-radius: 30px;
        width: fit-content;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0 3rem;
      }

      .download_container .download_text {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 1rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="main">
      <h1>About Project</h1>
      <div class="download_container">
        <p class="download_text"><%= count %> downloads</p>
      </div>
      <p>
        A simple Youtube Mp3 Downloader website, that uses Youtube Mp3 API, to
        get links of youtube videos. Links are then use to query another API to
        get download link. Application was written with the MERN Stack.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li class="headings">My struggles with the project:</li>
        <ol>
          <li>Navigating through the JSON response</li>
          <li>Enviromental file, not working as expected.</li>
          <li>EJS was tricky</li>
        </ol>
        <li class="headings">What I learned and improved with this project:</li>
        <ol>
          <li>Positioning, relative and absolute.</li>
          <li>Practice with CSS and HTML.</li>
          <li>Some HTML tags such as target.</li>
          <li>JavaScript File read and write.</li>
        </ol>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
